lead_paragraph: Northern Irishman Rory McIlroy capped a stunning comeback with a birdie at the fourth playoff hole to win the season-ending Tour Championship on Sunday, along with FedExCup honours and the mind-boggling $10 million bonus.

headline.print_headline: McIlroy Wins Tour Championship, $10 Million Bonus
